\ Comprehensive test for new introspection and system words

\ 1. typeof (Observer: should not consume)
5 typeof print
.s empty \ Should show 5

\ 2. Type predicates (Observer: should not consume)
3.14 float? print
.s empty \ Should show 3.14

\ 3. System words
pwd typeof print \ Should be 'str'
.s empty

"whoami" shell typeof print \ Should be 'str'
.s empty
